                            "field": "app_name",
                            "label": "Application Name(s) or ID(s)",
                            "help": "Leave blank to retrieve ALL applications. Each application is 1 API call per selected metric set (4 sets * 30 apps = 120 API calls). Please be mindful of the additional load on your AppD Controller.",
